207
00:08:59,706 --> 00:09:01,124
Aww!
Eu te disse!

208
00:09:02,125 --> 00:09:03,335
E aí, querida?

209
00:09:03,418 --> 00:09:05,796
Hum... quando você fizer
o tratamento,

210
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:08,173
